                    </li>
                    <li>Item 2</li>
                    <li>Item 3</li>
                </ul>

            <h4>5.2.4 Horizontal Lists</h4>

                <p>
                    Horizontal, or inline, lists are also supported. Often used as simple navigational menus. Subitems do not appear.
                </p>

                <ul class="horizontal">
                    <li>Item 1</li>
                    <li>Item 2</li>
                    <li>Item 3</li>
                </ul>

            <h4>5.2.5 Definition Lists</h4>

                <p>
                    Definition lists are useful for glossaries, dictionaries, and outlines. The tags <code>dl</code>, <code>dt</code>, and <code>dd</code> are used together to form the definition list. Definition lists are also used for marking up metadata.
                </p>

                <dl>
