        <h3>5.5 Addresses, Header, Footer, Aside, Section, Article, Nav</h3>

            <p>
                Addresses are commonly misunderstood elements. The <code>address</code> tag is used to indicate who to contact for a particular document. The tag is not used for arbitrary postal addresses and email address. Descovrir does not style the <code>address</code> tag.
            </p>

            <p>
                Other block tags such as header and footer are used for semantic representation, but receive no special styling.
            </p>

